<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta content="width=device-width" name="viewport">
  <title>Add claim: Incapacity Payments | MyService</title>
  <link href="docs/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid uikit-refactor">
  <noscript>
    <p role="alert">This website needs JavaScript to work properly.</p>
  </noscript>
  <nav class="uikit-skip-link">
    <a class="uikit-skip-link__link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a>
  </nav>
  <% include ../../../global/partials/header-topbar-new.ejs %>


  <main>
    <div id="main-content" class="section-feature border-bottom--mild margin-above--none margin-below--none padding-below">
      <div class="container margin-above--none">
        <h1 class="margin-above--none ss-align--center">
          <span class="heading">Required documents</span>
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-8">

          <div class="margin-above--extra margin-below--extra">

            <h3>We need you to provide some documents before we can determine your claim <span class="hint display-block">Accepted file types include pdf, jpeg and png. Maximum
                file size is 50MB.</span></h3>

            <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info margin-below--extra">
              <p>You can still submit this claim without providing the documents but we will need them eventually. You will have 28 days from the day you submit this
                claim to provide them.</p>
            </div>

            <h2>What we need</h2>

            <div class="mys-file-uploads__items">

              <!-- Tax file number declaration -->
              <div class="mys-file-uploads__item-border">
                <div class="mys-file-uploads__item mys-file-uploads__item--required">
                  <div class="mys-file-uploads__l-status">
                    <div class="mys-file-uploads__status mys-file-uploads__status--pending">
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__status-icon"></div>
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__status-sr">Success</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mys-file-uploads__info">
                    <div class="mys-file-uploads__info-item">
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__value">
                        <div><b>Tax file number declaration</b></div>
                        <div>You can get this form from the <a href="https://www.ato.gov.au/forms/tfn-declaration/" rel="external" target="_blank">ATO website</a>&nbsp;
                          <div class="tooltip">
                            <div id="gender-tt-label" class="tooltip__control" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-controls="gender-tt-message" aria-expanded="false">
                              <div class="tooltip__label tooltip__label--icon-only">
                                <a>Why do I need to provide this?</a>
                              </div>
                              <div class="tooltip__tab"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div id="gender-tt-message" class="tooltip__content" aria-labelledby="gender-tt-label" role="region" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
                              <div class="tooltip__message">The Tax file number declaration form allows us to work out how much tax to withhold from payments
                                we&nbsp;make&nbsp;to&nbsp;you.
                              </div>
                              <div class="tooltip__close" role="button" tabindex="0">Close</div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mys-file-uploads__item-actions">
                    <button class="mys-file-uploads__item-button uikit-btn small">Upload</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Medical Evidence -->
              <div class="mys-file-uploads__item-border">
                <div class="mys-file-uploads__item mys-file-uploads__item--required">
                  <div class="mys-file-uploads__l-status">
                    <div class="mys-file-uploads__status mys-file-uploads__status--pending">
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__status-icon"></div>
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__status-sr">Success</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mys-file-uploads__info">
                    <div class="mys-file-uploads__info-item">
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__value">
                        <div><b>Medical evidence</b></div>
                        <div>Get this from your treating practitioner.
                          <div class="tooltip">
                            <div id="gender-tt-label" class="tooltip__control" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-controls="gender-tt-message" aria-expanded="false">
                              <div class="tooltip__label tooltip__label--icon-only">
                                <a>Why do I need to provide this?</a>
                              </div>
                              <div class="tooltip__tab"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div id="gender-tt-message" class="tooltip__content" aria-labelledby="gender-tt-label" role="region" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
                              <div class="tooltip__message">Medical evidence lets us know the details around how your conditions are affecting your&nbsp;ability to work.
                              </div>
                              <div class="tooltip__close" role="button" tabindex="0">Close</div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mys-file-uploads__item-actions">
                    <button class="mys-file-uploads__item-button uikit-btn small">Upload</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Proof of employment -->
              <div class="mys-file-uploads__item-border mys-file-uploads__item-uploaded">
                <div class="mys-file-uploads__item">
                  <div class="mys-file-uploads__l-status">
                    <div class="mys-file-uploads__status mys-file-uploads__status--success">
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__status-icon"></div>
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__status-sr">Success</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mys-file-uploads__info">
                    <div class="mys-file-uploads__info-item">
                      <label class="mys-file-uploads__label">File name</label>
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__value">
                        <a href="#" class="">My document 222 AAA .png</a>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mys-file-uploads__info-item">
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__label">Document type</div>
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__value">
                        <div><b>Proof of civilian earnings</b></div>
                        <!-- <div>For example payslips or a copy of your current/last work contract.</div> -->
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mys-file-uploads__item-actions">
                    <button class="mys-file-uploads__item-button uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary small">Remove</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>



              <!-- Proof of medical discharge -->
              <div class="mys-file-uploads__item-border">
                <div class="mys-file-uploads__item mys-file-uploads__item--required">
                  <div class="mys-file-uploads__l-status">
                    <div class="mys-file-uploads__status mys-file-uploads__status--pending">
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__status-icon"></div>
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__status-sr">Success</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mys-file-uploads__info">
                    <div class="mys-file-uploads__info-item">
                      <div class="mys-file-uploads__value">
                        <div><b>Proof of military earnings</b></div>
                        <div>Provide your SVA (Military Pay Advice) with allowances
                          <div class="tooltip">
                            <div id="gender-tt-label" class="tooltip__control" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-controls="gender-tt-message" aria-expanded="false">
                              <div class="tooltip__label tooltip__label--icon-only">
                                <a>Why do I need to provide this?</a>
                              </div>
                              <div class="tooltip__tab"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div id="gender-tt-message" class="tooltip__content" aria-labelledby="gender-tt-label" role="region" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
                              <div class="tooltip__message">This allows us to determine your normal earnings.
                              </div>
                              <div class="tooltip__close" role="button" tabindex="0">Close</div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>

                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mys-file-uploads__item-actions">
                    <button class="mys-file-uploads__item-button uikit-btn small">Upload</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>

          </div>

          <div class="pagination pagination--ss-reverse-order">
            <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary btnPrev" id="btnPrev">Previous</button>
            <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/claims'">Back to Claims</button>
            <div class="floated">
              <button class="uikit-btn btnNext" id="btnNext">Save and next</button>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>


      </div>
    </div>

    <% include ../partials/cancel-modal.ejs %>
    </div>

  </main>

  <% include ../../../global/partials/footer.ejs %>


  <script>




    $(Document).ready(function () {
      $("#btnPrev").click(function () { window.location.href = "/incap-8" });
      $("#btnNext").click(function () { window.location.href = "/incap-10" });

      // Show and hide needs list
      $("#leaving-yes").click(function () {
        $(".leaving-date").show("fast");
        $(".save-and-next").hide();
      });
      $("#leaving-no").click(function () {
        $(".leaving-date").hide();
        $(".save-and-next").show("fast");
      });

    });
  </script>

</body>

</html>